  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support 600 rural children to school in Nigeria</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Bridge Leadership Foundation plans to send 600 rural children to school in Bakassi and Akpabuyo communities of Cross River State who cannot otherwise afford education or have no parents/guardian to cater for them. The project will setup learning support centers to provide literacy support services and enroll them to schools on partial and full time scholarship. Your donations will go towards setting up 6 centers, school fees, uniforms, sandals, socks, text books, and notebooks</narrative>
  </description>
